You shouldn't.

00:09:25.820 --> 00:09:27.403
But some of those
things, I keep it up

00:09:27.403 --> 00:09:29.070
to remind myself of
where I came from

00:09:29.070 --> 00:09:30.670
and who I was in that moment.

00:09:30.670 --> 00:09:34.410
And I like even thinking about
high school essays that I won,

00:09:34.410 --> 00:09:38.870
I won like two major essay
contests in high school

00:09:38.870 --> 00:09:43.600
writing an essay
on whether people

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:44.942
