00:10:46.032 --> 00:10:48.240
But I wake up with an entire
post in my head already,

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:50.650
and I'm just like, ah, OK, cool.

00:10:50.650 --> 00:10:52.580
So in that way, I'm
writing for myself.

00:10:52.580 --> 00:10:56.271
But also I'm writing for people
to consume it and hopefully

00:10:56.271 --> 00:10:57.270
change hearts and minds.

00:10:57.270 --> 00:11:00.700
Because I'm also not trying to
write to preach to the choir

00:11:00.700 --> 00:11:01.477
all the time.

00:11:01.477 --> 00:11:03.560
Because it's like at that
point, what's the point?

00:11:03.560 --> 00:11:06.020
So it's a combination.

00:11:06.020 --> 00:11:09.430
BRADLEY HOROWITZ: So you're
an early technology adopter,

00:11:09.430 --> 00:11:13.850
early-on on blogspot,
early with blogging.

00:11:13.850 --> 00:11:14.990
