00:11:14.990 --> 00:11:19.140
Like where are you at on
vlogging, Snapchat, Instagram,

00:11:19.140 --> 00:11:19.960
Twitter?

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:22.930
Like are there enough hours
in the day to sort of--

00:11:22.930 --> 00:11:25.263
LUVVIE AJAYI: No, there are
not enough hours in the day.

00:11:25.263 --> 00:11:27.625
And I am officially feeling
like the oldie in tech.

00:11:27.625 --> 00:11:28.125
Because--

00:11:28.125 --> 00:11:29.833
BRADLEY HOROWITZ:
Well, I mean 13 years--

00:11:29.833 --> 00:11:31.694
LUVVIE AJAYI: 13 years--
come on-- veteran.

00:11:31.694 --> 00:11:37.140
[LAUGHING] But there are certain
platforms I cannot get with,

00:11:37.140 --> 00:11:39.370
even though I've tried, and
I'm a digital strategist,

00:11:39.370 --> 00:11:40.703
and I can see the value in them.

00:11:40.703 --> 00:11:44.870
But me personally, me,
myself, and I personally, I

00:11:44.870 --> 00:11:47.470
have a trouble infusing
it into my day.

00:11:47.470 --> 00:11:48.910
Snapchat is one of them.

00:11:48.910 --> 00:11:52.190
I have tried, you guys.

00:11:52.190 --> 00:11:53.960
Snapchat-- so here's
the thing that I

00:11:53.960 --> 00:11:55.930
have a problem with
Generation Millennia

00:11:55.930 --> 00:11:59.350
and Generation Social Media,
which I'm a very firm part of,

00:11:59.350 --> 00:12:02.080
is we feel like everything
we do is interesting.

00:12:02.080 --> 00:12:02.810
And it's not.

00:12:02.810 --> 00:12:03.782
[LAUGHTER]

00:12:03.782 --> 00:12:06.630
So like people all spend
all day on Snapchat

00:12:06.630 --> 00:12:08.005
telling you exactly
what they did

00:12:08.005 --> 00:12:10.050
in every moment of their day.

00:12:10.050 --> 00:12:11.910
And I'll log into
Snapchat, and I'll just

00:12:11.910 --> 00:12:12.200
be like, you know what?

00:12:12.200 --> 00:12:13.991
Today's the day I'm
going to give it a try.

00:12:13.991 --> 00:12:15.385
And I'm going to scroll through.

00:12:15.385 --> 00:12:16.760
And people are
walking to the bus

00:12:16.760 --> 00:12:19.970
like, yes, I'm walking
to the bus stop.

00:12:19.970 --> 00:12:20.780
OK.

00:12:20.780 --> 00:12:21.442
And?

00:12:21.442 --> 00:12:23.650
And then the filters are
killing me softly, you guys.

00:12:23.650 --> 00:12:27.020
Like the filters, the flower
filter, the face-- I'm just

00:12:27.020 --> 00:12:29.770
like, why does everybody look
like a cartoon right now?

00:12:29.770 --> 00:12:32.550
So I have a Snapshot account,
but I log into it like once

00:12:32.550 --> 00:12:33.220
a month.

00:12:33.220 --> 00:12:35.950
And I think I've
Snapchatted twice total.

00:12:35.950 --> 00:12:39.650
And I do actually have
a Snapchattable life,

00:12:39.650 --> 00:12:41.110
because I'm in
these random rooms.

00:12:41.110 --> 00:12:42.970
I call myself Forrest Gump.

00:12:42.970 --> 00:12:44.870
I do all these
interesting things.

00:12:44.870 --> 00:12:46.078
BRADLEY HOROWITZ: That's you?

00:12:46.078 --> 00:12:48.620
LUVVIE AJAYI: [LAUGHING]
Right, like can you believe it?

00:12:48.620 --> 00:12:52.479
But it's like, catch me on
Instagram, catch me on Twitter.

00:12:52.479 --> 00:12:53.020
I'm on there.

00:12:53.020 --> 00:12:54.620
Catch me on Facebook.

00:12:54.620 --> 00:12:58.400
To add Snapchat to it to
catch a moment-by-moment thing

00:12:58.400 --> 00:12:59.992
of my day is just a lot.

00:12:59.992 --> 00:13:00.950
BRADLEY HOROWITZ: Yeah.

00:13:00.950 --> 00:13:04.030
And what about vlogging
or YouTube or--?

00:13:04.030 --> 00:13:07.034
LUVVIE AJAYI: I have
actively rejected YouTube.

00:13:07.034 --> 00:13:07.950
BRADLEY HOROWITZ: Why?

00:13:07.950 --> 00:13:08.710
AUDIENCE: [GASPS]

00:13:08.710 --> 00:13:10.396
LUVVIE AJAYI: Yup, I have.

00:13:10.396 --> 00:13:12.050
Yup, I said it.

00:13:12.050 --> 00:13:14.562
[LAUGHING] At Google.

00:13:14.562 --> 00:13:18.970
[LAUGHING] I've made it a
point not to be on YouTube,

00:13:18.970 --> 00:13:21.120
because I don't like the
community on YouTube.

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:21.930
BRADLEY HOROWITZ:
Well, this is something

00:13:21.930 --> 00:13:22.900
I wanted to talk about.

00:13:22.900 --> 00:13:26.000
Because social media
has tons of es.

