This morning my wife
showed me a site

00:17:58.760 --> 00:18:00.840
called FriendsWhoLikeTrump.com.

00:18:00.840 --> 00:18:02.510
I don't know if
you've seen this.

00:18:02.510 --> 00:18:05.250
But it actually exposes
your Facebook friends

00:18:05.250 --> 00:18:06.670
who have actually liked Trump.

00:18:06.670 --> 00:18:08.480
So I did a bit of
unfriending this morning.

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:09.271
LUVVIE AJAYI: Amen.

