you've been on this Earth.

00:34:39.960 --> 00:34:42.346
So you just kind of
got to commit to it.

00:34:42.346 --> 00:34:43.429
It's not going to be easy.

00:34:43.429 --> 00:34:45.906
It's a drop-kick to your
ego when you realize

00:34:45.906 --> 00:34:47.030
