00:34:47.030 --> 00:34:47.530
It is.

00:34:47.530 --> 00:34:50.260
It's like, damn, I didn't
know I was that person.

00:34:50.260 --> 00:34:51.710
You are.

00:34:51.710 --> 00:34:53.889
Now, now that you know that
